did.unittitle: Identified as "Russell Cave"; Students, teacher, and Superintendent Massillon Alexander (M.A.) Cassidy in front of white school house. The second row is standing on benches. A young girl holds a slated board that reads " Russell Cave Dist 6 Miss Alice Moore Teacher" A handwritten note beneath the photo states "New house here". A piece of note paper also states "L to R 1 row- 7th Hetttie DeLong (Mrs. Wm Tucker) 13 Miss Alice Moore Teacher"
